Nonono! Erud's tonic is one of the components you need to get the book. You can get Frostbite to cough up the fish, but you need to go to Surefall glade to the fella inside the hollow tree. (Zone in, follow around to the right, you'll see it) Talk to him to get a flask of nitrates that is supposed to go to some farmer in the Karanas. Take it instead to the Ak'Anon zoo and give it to Kimble. (Watch your faction here...) He'll give you a regurgitonic which is what you give to Frostbite to get the fish. It's time consuming, but when I hear about people who have spent untold hours trying to kill the fish in Qeynos, I just have to laugh. I got all kinds of stuff, met all kinds of people and generally had a good time just on the Fish part of this quest, not to mention the experience, and no negative faction hits for getting the fish.<BR>
